    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single below-required factor (Test conditions, achieved 1 vs required 2) is accepted given the quasi-static nature of the COU and published insensitivity of titanium alloy constructs to loading rate in this regime. All three QoIs satisfy pre-established acceptance bounds. Overall credibility is sufficient to support regulatory use of the FEA framework for this COU.",
